item.title: About Paisley Parker
item.description: Howdy there! I am Paisley Parker and I am an enby model. Enby means that I am gender non-binary, identifying as neither male nor female but something across the spectrum. I am located in the South West United States and I love hot desert days. Currently I produce a mix of art and adult oriented content all of which is available for purchase. You will notice that although I have a penis, I produce both masculine and feminine content with a trend towards trans feminine.
